{
  "name": "AI Customer Support Agent (RAG + WhatsApp / Telegram)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "sticky-1",
      "name": "ðŸ“’ Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-800, -300],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AI Customer Support Agent\n\nThis workflow creates an AI-powered customer support assistant using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).\n\n**Channels Supported**:\n- WhatsApp\n- Telegram\n\n**Capabilities**:\n- Answers customer questions from your documents\n- Uses AI (GPT / Gemini)\n- Escalates to a human when confidence is low\n\nIdeal for clinics, SaaS, and local businesses."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "webhook-1",
      "name": "Incoming Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "position": [-600, 0],
      "parameters": {
        "path": "ai-support-agent",
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "responseMode": "onReceived"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-2",
      "name": "ðŸ“’ Channel Normalization",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-400, -300],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Channel Normalization\n\nThis step normalizes incoming messages from WhatsApp or Telegram into a common format so the rest of the workflow remains channel-agnostic."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "set-1",
      "name": "Normalize Input",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "position": [-400, 0],
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "name": "userMessage",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.message || $json.body.text }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "name": "userId",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.from || $json.body.chat_id }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-3",
      "name": "ðŸ“’ Knowledge Retrieval (RAG)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-200, -300],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Knowledge Retrieval (RAG)\n\nThis node retrieves relevant knowledge chunks from your vector database.\n\nYou can connect:\n- Google Drive\n- Notion\n- Any vector DB (Qdrant, Pinecone, Supabase)\n\nNo credentials are hardcoded."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "http-1",
      "name": "Retrieve Knowledge",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "position": [-200, 0],
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.VECTOR_DB_ENDPOINT }}",
        "method": "POST",
        "authentication": "none",
        "jsonParameters": true,
        "options": {},
        "bodyParametersJson": "={ \"query\": $json.userMessage }"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-4",
      "name": "ðŸ“’ AI Response Generation",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [100, -300],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AI Response Generation\n\nThis node generates a response using GPT or Gemini.\n\nThe model is instructed to:\n- Use retrieved context\n- Answer clearly\n- Provide a confidence score (0â€“1)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ai-1",
      "name": "Generate AI Answer",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "position": [100, 0],
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
        "messages": [
          {
            "role": "system",
            "content": "You are a customer support AI. Answer using the provided context. Return JSON with fields: answer, confidence (0 to 1)."
          },
          {
            "role": "user",
            "content": "Question: {{ $json.userMessage }}\n\nContext: {{ $json.data }}"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-5",
      "name": "ðŸ“’ Confidence Check",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [400, -300],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Confidence Check\n\nIf the AI confidence score is below the threshold, the message is escalated to a human operator."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "if-1",
      "name": "Low Confidence?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "position": [400, 0],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "number": [
            {
              "value1": "={{ $json.confidence }}",
              "operation": "smaller",
              "value2": 0.6
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-6",
      "name": "ðŸ“’ Human Escalation",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [650, -200],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Human Escalation\n\nLow-confidence queries are forwarded to a human via Slack, email, or CRM.\n\nThis ensures quality and trust."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "slack-1",
      "name": "Notify Human Agent",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.slack",
      "position": [650, 0],
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "message",
        "operation": "post",
        "channel": "support-escalation",
        "text": "Low confidence AI query:\n\nUser: {{ $json.userId }}\nMessage: {{ $json.userMessage }}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-7",
      "name": "ðŸ“’ Send AI Reply",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [650, 200],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Send AI Reply\n\nHigh-confidence AI responses are sent back to the user via WhatsApp or Telegram."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "http-2",
      "name": "Send Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "position": [650, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.MESSAGE_API_ENDPOINT }}",
        "method": "POST",
        "jsonParameters": true,
        "authentication": "none",
        "bodyParametersJson": "={ \"to\": $json.userId, \"message\": $json.answer }"
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Incoming Message": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Normalize Input", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Normalize Input": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Retrieve Knowledge", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Retrieve Knowledge": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Generate AI Answer", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Generate AI Answer": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Low Confidence?", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Low Confidence?": {
      "main": [
        [{ "node": "Notify Human Agent", "type": "main", "index": 0 }],
        [{ "node": "Send Message", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]
      ]
    }
  }
}
